    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 12,
      "width": 24,
      "height": 1,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Backpressure & Stream Processor Latency\n*8.7 exposes `zeebe_backpressure_requests_limit` (gauge) and the stream-processor latency histogram. The 8.8 inflight/dropped metrics don't exist on 8.7 \u2014 those panels were removed.*"
      }
    },
